      <title>赫斯投资者 D.E.肖将放弃对雪佛龙交易的投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/hess-hes-investor-d-e-shaw-to-abstain-from-vote-on-chevron-cvx-merger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[D.E.萧氏作为赫斯公司 (Hess Corp.) 15 大股东之一，该公司计划在雪佛龙公司 (Chevron Corp.) 以 530 亿美元收购这家石油公司的交易中放弃投票，成为本周第二个站出来反对该交易的主要投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/hess-hes-investor-d-e-shaw-to-abstain-from-vote-on-chevron-cvx-merger</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 15:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>跨国公司正在寻求针对墨西哥“超级比索”的保护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/multinationals-are-seeking-currency-protection-against-mexican-super-peso</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于许多在墨西哥开展业务的美国公司来说，经济活动带来的好处的另一面是比索飙升带来的日益沉重的负担，从而提高了采取积极的货币对冲策略的必要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-17/multinationals-are-seeking-currency-protection-against-mexican-super-peso</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 May 2024 14:56:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
